  "body": "Hello. I am trying to run go-ethereum on my WSL (Ubuntu). I want to change the blockchain storage directory to my external HDD. I am doing the following:\r\n\r\n`geth --datadir \"/mnt/t/ethereum_data\" console`\r\n\r\nBut I get an error:\r\n\r\n```\r\nWARN [10-20|20:17:31.923] IPC opening failed\r\nurl=/mnt/t/ethereum_data/geth.ipc error=\"listen unix /mnt/t/ethereum_data/geth.ipc: bind: operation not supported\"\r\nFatal: Error starting protocol stack: listen unix /mnt/t/ethereum_data/geth.ipc: bind: operation not supported\r\n```\r\n\r\nIf I run the standard \"`geth console`\", everything works fine.\r\nPlease help.",
